{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":false,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"aria-colindextext","mdn_url":"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-colindextext","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>The <code>aria-colindextext</code> attribute defines a human readable text alternative of the numeric <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-colindex\"><code>aria-colindex</code></a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"description","title":"Description","isH3":false,"content":"<p>When you have a very large table or when you purposefully want to display just a section of a table, not all columns may be present in the DOM. When this happens, we use the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-colcount\"><code>aria-colcount</code></a> with an integer value to define how many columns the table (or grid) would have if all the columns were present and add the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-colindex\"><code>aria-colindex</code></a> property on each column to provide information on the column index within that larger table.</p>\n<p>In the following HTML snippet, our table has 8 columns, but we are only displaying 4. The \"city\" column is the fifth column of our larger table, as defined by <code>aria-colindex=\"5\"</code>.</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>table</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">aria-colcount</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>8<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>thead</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>tr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>th</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">aria-colindex</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>1<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">scope</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>col<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>First name<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>th</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>th</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">aria-colindex</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>2<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">scope</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>col<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Last name<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>th</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>th</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">aria-colindex</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>5<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">scope</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>col<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>City<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>th</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>th</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">aria-colindex</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>7<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">scope</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>col<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Zip<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>th</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>tr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>thead</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  …\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>table</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>This table is not very complex. Had this been a 100+ column spreadsheet or a grid without column headers, such as a chess board, the provided or calculated value of <code>aria-colindex</code> might not be meaningful or may not reflect the displayed index. When this is the case, <code>aria-colindextext</code> can be included. The value is a string that is a human readable text alternative to the numeric <code>aria-colindex</code>.</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>table</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">aria-colcount</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>128<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>thead</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>tr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>th</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">aria-colindex</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>1<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">aria-colindextext</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>NYSE stock symbol<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">scope</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>col<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n        NYSE\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>th</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>th</span>\n        <span class=\"token attr-name\">aria-colindex</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>110<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n        <span class=\"token attr-name\">aria-colindextext</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>Value at start of 2021<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n        <span class=\"token attr-name\">scope</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>col<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n        01/21\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>th</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>th</span>\n        <span class=\"token attr-name\">aria-colindex</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>122<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n        <span class=\"token attr-name\">aria-colindextext</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>Value at start of 2022<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n        <span class=\"token attr-name\">scope</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>col<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n        01/22\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>th</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>th</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">aria-colindex</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>124<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">scope</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>col<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Recommendation<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>th</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>tr</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>thead</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  …\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>table</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>In the above example, the table has 128 columns of which only 4 columns are shown. The <code>aria-colindextext</code> is used in three columns to provide human readable text alternatives. By including <code>aria-colindextext=\"Value at start of 2021\"</code>, assistive technologies can announce \"Value at start of 2021\" instead of \"Column 110\".</p>\n<p>Only use <code>aria-colindextext</code> when the provided or calculated value of <code>aria-colindex</code> is not meaningful or does not reflect the displayed index. Whenever you include <code>aria-colindextext</code>, also keep the <code>aria-colindex</code> as some assistive technologies rely on the numeric column index for the purpose of keeping track of the user's position and in providing alternative table navigation.</p>\n<div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\">\n  <p><strong>Note:</strong> While <code>aria-colindex</code> can be added to a row when all the columns present are contiguous as sequential values can be deduced, <code>aria-colindextext</code> is NOT a supported property of <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/row_role\"><code>row</code></a>.</p>\n</div>\n<p>See related <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-rowindextext\"><code>aria-rowindextext</code></a>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"values","title":"Values","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><code>&lt;string&gt;</code>\n    <ul>\n      <li>The human readable text alternative of the numeric <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-colindex\"><code>aria-colindex</code></a></li>\n    </ul>\n  </li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"ariamixin_api","title":"ARIAMixin API","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"element.ariacolindextext\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/ariaColIndexText\"><code>Element.ariaColIndexText</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>The <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/ariaColIndexText\"><code>ariaColIndexText</code></a> property, part of the <a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"The documentation about this has not yet been written; please consider contributing!\"><code>ARIAMixin</code></a> interface, reflects the value of the <code>aria-colindextext</code> attribute, which defines a human readable text alternative of aria-colindex.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"associated_roles","title":"Associated roles","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Used in roles:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/cell_role\"><code>cell</code></a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Inherits into roles:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/columnheader_role\"><code>columnheader</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/columnheader_role\"><code>rowheader</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Specifications","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://w3c.github.io/aria/#aria-colindextext","title":"Accessible Rich Internet Applications (WAI-ARIA) 1.2"}],"query":"undefined"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"See Also","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Element/ariaColIndexText\"><code>Element.ariaColIndexText</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-colindex\"><code>aria-colindex</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-rowindextext\"><code>aria-rowindextext</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-colcount\"><code>aria-colcount</code></a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/cell_role\"><code>cell</code> role</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/columnheader_role\"><code>columnheader</code> role</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Roles/columnheader_role\"><code>rowheader</code> role</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Description","id":"description"},{"text":"Values","id":"values"},{"text":"ARIAMixin API","id":"ariamixin_api"},{"text":"Associated roles","id":"associated_roles"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"See Also","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"The aria-colindextext attribute defines a human readable text alternative of the numeric aria-colindex.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-09-13T12:22:39.000Z","source":{"folder":"en-us/web/accessibility/aria/attributes/aria-colindextext","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/blob/style/old/files/en-us/web/accessibility/aria/attributes/aria-colindextext/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/commit/7d2071f78f38f8be38888a32c599aebba348941b","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web","title":"Web technology for developers"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility","title":"Accessibility"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA","title":"ARIA"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes","title":"ARIA states and properties"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA/Attributes/aria-colindextext","title":"aria-colindextext"}],"pageTitle":"aria-colindextext - Accessibility | MDN","noIndexing":false}}